{"tid":2370294,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解DSE搞左多咁多年仲未廢除小組形式既口試","createTime":"2021-01-18T02:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T10:06:48.000Z","uid":142854,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2d8fffa1ee63acbef2d7e146f4f1afd7c4b1ba","tid":2370294,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:35:42.000Z","msg":"一來題目難度差距大<br />\n二來組員質疑參差<br />\n三來座位次序會影響首輪論點俾既分 <br />\n<br />\n成個考試一半考口才 一半考運氣<br />\n<br />\n大部分組成個討論落係其中一兩個人之間搶黎搶去<br />\n想問下呢個年代有邊間公司開會係咁<br />\n<br />\n有啲人搶到個發言權就一輪嘴講埋哂d廢話 仲要一邊講一邊諗 errr ... errr 你打斷佢既廢話佢會同你鬥長氣 鬥到一邊停為止<br />\n<br />\n有時你講左個靚point D人就起勢衝埋黎想執雞打斷你 再自己講返d垃圾<br />\n<br />\n考完之後不斷同人講自己1+3 1+4 1+5<br />\n呢樣野到底邊個諗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d718154b810a9f23f650ecf986f777fe11b252","tid":2370294,"uid":368454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:37:04.000Z","msg":"廢左啦 樓主訓左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a24726d7f2d6a53870f1014e3fc474e7e4b2e9","tid":2370294,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:38:03.000Z","msg":"樓豬中學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357e1806edb4d6cfd1040c8b155305c5a26b2f89","tid":2370294,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"32d718154b810a9f23f650ecf986f777fe11b252","tid":2370294,"uid":368454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:37:04.000Z","msg":"廢左啦 樓主訓左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:39:24.000Z","msg":"因為今年特別先取消姐<br />\n下年無事咪又搞返"},{"pid":"41029640fe528d36ec2911825917ec4a7f9a6ad7","tid":2370294,"uid":142854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99a24726d7f2d6a53870f1014e3fc474e7e4b2e9","tid":2